    "description": "Swords and Bones 3 is a game inspired by 80s and 90s action-platformer games with a modern and polished level design. Off course, all in pixel-art!<br>In the game you will take on the role of a young rogue, able to move with much more agility than the heroes of the previous two chapters.<br>A long journey awaits you: from the dungeon to the lair of the last boss; you will face a series of levels filled with traps and nasty enemies. <br>In Swords &amp; Bones, you will put your skills to the test thanks to a balanced and never unfair difficulty.<br>Each enemy you annihilate will earn you coins to spend on new spells, items and power-ups!<br>Will you be able to win the whole game and see the real ending?<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A new story!<br></li><li>Dodge attacks and boosts your agility!<br></li><li>Use combos to annihilate enemies!<br></li><li>Improved graphics!<br></li><li>4 new devastating spells to master!<br></li><li>Power up your hero collecting coins!<br></li><li>Over 50 action-packed levels!<br></li><li>6 fearsome bosses ready to fight!<br></li><li>Two endings to discover!<br></li><li>Pixel-art graphics in 16-bit style!<br></li><li>An epic and dark chiptune soundtrack!<br></li><li>Achievements!</li></ul>",
